    <item>
      <title>i love the story behind this project, I got this analog color corrector while I ...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DJq17g7Nz2D/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/497709584_1218481816409646_3986474771048434180_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=108&amp;ig_cache_key=MzYzMjk1MzIzNTY5NTE1NjYxMQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgxMTM2LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=h7dXEXOiBpYQ7kNvwEvAUd7&amp;_nc_oc=AdruXkqo9vu0BeFjuIXit1lreiq4GIZ7a1fsfP9Qa5V9kULYKKL3N8mUiwZxYOWjnqs&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=qbsA-eCmmVfxmsU4RGj2Mw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzdLlzRk0RZWmOQpnOOHIXjo_mFP_owHZYXgeqgA2uqVA&amp;oe=69C95E9B" alt="Instagram billede fra @lecronachedidave" /></p><p><strong>@lecronachedidave</strong></p><p>i love the story behind this project, I got this analog color corrector while I was travelling around Italy sleeping on the back of my dad’s pick up when I casually passed by a thrift shop in the middle of nowhere and in a corner here it is, a Sony XV-C900 for 25€! <br/>
<br/>
I took it with me for the rest of the trip and months later, back home in Milan, I saw a @technopooch video and decided to try this magic tv thing. I grabbed my dad old handycam, a ctr tv I got for free and boom! The video blew overnight, got me featured on the @hypebeast page and kinda of turned my life around, connecting me with a whole new world! <br/>
<br/>
Now I’m starting to take this content creation thing more seriously since u all are giving me mad support so, thanks! Let’s see where it brings me, because I love good stories :) <br/>
<br/>
#tutorial #retrotech #videoart #analog #ctr #vhs</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/497709584_1218481816409646_3986474771048434180_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=108&amp;ig_cache_key=MzYzMjk1MzIzNTY5NTE1NjYxMQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgxMTM2LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=h7dXEXOiBpYQ7kNvwEvAUd7&amp;_nc_oc=AdruXkqo9vu0BeFjuIXit1lreiq4GIZ7a1fsfP9Qa5V9kULYKKL3N8mUiwZxYOWjnqs&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=qbsA-eCmmVfxmsU4RGj2Mw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzdLlzRk0RZWmOQpnOOHIXjo_mFP_owHZYXgeqgA2uqVA&amp;oe=69C95E9B" alt="Instagram billede fra @lecronachedidave" /></p><p><strong>@lecronachedidave</strong></p><p>i love the story behind this project, I got this analog color corrector while I was travelling around Italy sleeping on the back of my dad’s pick up when I casually passed by a thrift shop in the middle of nowhere and in a corner here it is, a Sony XV-C900 for 25€! <br/>
<br/>
I took it with me for the rest of the trip and months later, back home in Milan, I saw a @technopooch video and decided to try this magic tv thing. I grabbed my dad old handycam, a ctr tv I got for free and boom! The video blew overnight, got me featured on the @hypebeast page and kinda of turned my life around, connecting me with a whole new world! <br/>
<br/>
Now I’m starting to take this content creation thing more seriously since u all are giving me mad support so, thanks! Let’s see where it brings me, because I love good stories :) <br/>
<br/>
#tutorial #retrotech #videoart #analog #ctr #vhs</p>]]></content:encoded>
